Setup
We prepare the auxiliary variable \(W\) (lagged outcome at period 1) for the Covariate Unconfoundedness assumption:

W_df &lt;- nlsy_wagescars |&gt;
  filter(period == 1) |&gt;
  select(id, W = lwage)

panel &lt;- nlsy_wagescars |&gt;
  left_join(W_df, by = "id")
